         <div type="translation" source="#irt2009" xml:lang="en">
            
            <p>To a lover of his country and of his fellow-citizens, because by the emperor's concession he presented to his fellow-citizens four living tusked beasts <note>elephants</note>. By decree of the most splendid city council they voted a two-horse chariot. <supplied reason="subaudible">In honour</supplied> of Porfyrius, of Porfyrius.</p></div>
